{"tid":471921,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（環保系列）支持 「裸買運動」","createTime":"2017-11-17T16:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T04:53:01.000Z","uid":24629,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f60e659c781f1d53f929649f23785f12e4d72a46","tid":471921,"uid":24629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"為協助商場減少垃圾費開支，早前曾在中西區舉辦「裸買運動」鼓勵食客自攜器皿外賣的思網絡，計劃在葵涌廣場再推動「裸買」，初步有60間食肆表示支持。思網絡總監鄭敏華指，大部份食肆願意配合計劃，個別食肆更願意向自攜器皿的食客提供優惠，例如多給一粒魚蛋、牛柳或減價2元等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/133145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F133145&d=9jjekClNMuLH3TYA%2FbvXeMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ae814cc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/133145</a>"},{"pid":"e292cbc27df60681155a622a23e40f11c75ec7c3","tid":471921,"uid":89954,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"支持 但係俾多一粒魚蛋呢個優惠吸引力真係幾低"},{"pid":"7727298209f6634bd28317a51e222f1f1f5f75c0","tid":471921,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持 但係俾多一粒魚蛋呢個優惠吸引力真係幾低</blockquote><br />\n我覺得ok，吸引到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da44c0253df68d8dd79406c351f4dad9ee1265e","tid":471921,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:53:01.000Z","msg":"帶個碟/兜去佢俾飯菜我?"}]}